snippet.title: SHOWER:  Shower With Your Dad Simulator 2015 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Help bring this game to steam by voting for it on steam greenlight, as it's the game pc gamers truly deserve.

http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=404111723

Do YOU still shower with your dad?


A collaborative #SAGameDev effort, in the pursuit of ushering in a new era of games.

Music by @JamesRossiAudio and @blastron, full track available at https://soundcloud.com/mint-pixel/shower-feat-james-rossi
